<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html>
    <head>
        <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
		<title>PureText Newsletter</title>
		<style type="text/CSS">
            {literal}
                /*The .ExternalClass is used for Hotmail and ensures your email will take up the entire width of its viewing pane.*/
                .ExternalClass {width:100%;}
                /*The .yshortcuts {color: #F00;} is for Yahoo Classic and Yahoo New. Set this to be the color you prefer for your links.*/
                .yshortcuts {color: #F00;}
                p {margin:0; padding:0; margin-bottom:0;} /*optional*/
                a, a:link, a:visited {color:#2A5DB0;} /*optional*/
                /*The iPhone and iPad auto scales small fonts up to 12px. This bit of code makes text display as intended but means it is still scaleable.*/
                div, p, a, li, td { -webkit-text-size-adjust:100%; }
            {/literal}
    	</style>
	</head>
<body style="margin: 0">
<!-- Start of preheader container -->
<table width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
		<td valign="middle" height="60" bgcolor="#000000" align="center">
			<!-- Start of preheader -->
			<table width="600" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="20" border="0" align="center">
				<tr>
					<td>
					    <p style="font-size: 10px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #CCCCCC;text-align: left;">Generated at {date('l jS \of F Y h:i:s A')}</p>
						<p style="font-size: 10px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #CCCCCC;text-align: left;">
						Having trouble reading this email?
						<a target="_blank" style="color:#CCCCCC" href="{$magic_web_root}Mail/view/{$mail_instance_id}">click here</a> to view it in your browser.
						</p>
					</td>
				</tr>
			</table>
			<!-- End of preheader -->
		</td>
	</tr>
</table>
<!-- End of header precontainer -->
<!-- Start of header container -->
<table width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
		<td valign="top" bgcolor="#000000">
			<!-- Start of header -->
			<table width="600" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="20" border="0" align="center">
				<tr>
					<td>
						<p style="font-size: 40px; font-family: Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif; letter-spacing: -3px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #FFFFFF;text-align: left;">{$heading}</p>
					</td>
				</tr>
			</table>
			<!-- End of header -->
		</td>
	</tr>
</table>
<!-- End of header container -->
<!-- Start of intro copy -->
<table width="600" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
		<td valign="top" style="padding-top: 25px; padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 25px;padding-left: 20px">
			<p style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif; line-height: 26px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #444444;">
			{$message}
			</p>
		</td>
	</tr>
</table>
<!-- End of intro copy -->
<!-- Start of main container -->
<table width="600" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="center">
	<tr>
		
		<!-- Start of Main Column -->
		<td width="600" valign="top">
			<table width="400" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="left">
				<tr>
					<td width="360" valign="top" style="padding-top: 0; padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 20px;padding-left: 20px">
						<h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif; font-weight: lighter; margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 3px; color: #444444 !important;text-align: left;">Trace</h2>
						<p style="font-size: 11px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #444444;text-align: left;"><pre>{$trace}</pre></p>
					</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td width="360" valign="top" style="padding-top: 0; padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 20px;padding-left: 20px">
						<h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif; font-weight: lighter; margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 3px; color: #444444 !important;text-align: left;">Request</h2>
						<p style="font-size: 11px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #444444;text-align: left;">
						    Path: {$request_path}<br />
						    From: {$request_from}<br />
						    Browser: {$request_browser}
						</p>
					</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td width="360" valign="top" style="padding-top: 0; padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 20px;padding-left: 20px">
						<h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif; font-weight: lighter;  margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 3px; color: #444444 !important;text-align: left;">Nullam porttitor ligula</h2>
						<p style="font-size: 11px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #444444;text-align: left;">Donec porttitor ligula eu dolor. Maecenas vitae nulla consequat libero cursus venenatis. Nam magna enim, accumsan eu, blandit sed, blandit a, eros. <a target="_blank" href="">Read more</a></p>
					</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td width="360" valign="top" style="padding-top: 0; padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 20px;padding-left: 20px">
						<h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif; font-weight: lighter; margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 3px; color: #444444 !important;text-align: left;">Mauris aliquet mattis</h2>
						<p style="font-size: 11px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #444444;text-align: left;">Quisque facilisis erat a dui. Nam malesuada ornare dolor. Cras gravida, diam sit amet rhoncus ornare, erat elit consectetuer erat, id egestas pede nibh eget odio. Proin tincidunt, velit vel porta elementum, magna diam molestie sapien, non aliquet massa pede eu diam. <a target="_blank" href="">Read more</a>
					</td>
				</tr>

			</table>
		</td>
		<!-- End of Main Column -->
	</tr>
</table>
<!-- End of main container -->
<!-- Start of footer container -->
<table width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center" style="padding-top: 20px">
	<tr>
		<td>
			<table width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
				<tr>
					<td valign="top" height="60" bgcolor="#F5F5F5" align="center">
						<!-- Start of footer -->
						<table width="600" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="20" align="center">
							<tr>
								<td valign="top" width="160" style="padding-top: 20px; padding-right: 20px;padding-bottom: 30px;padding-left: 20px">
									<h2 style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Tahoma,Geneva,sans-serif; font-weight: lighter; margin: 0px; padding-bottom: 3px; color: #444444 !important;text-align: left;">Why have I been sent this email?</h2>
									<p style="font-size: 10px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #444444;text-align: left;">
									You were sent this email because you are listed as a support email inbox.
									</p>
								</td>
							</tr>
						</table>
						<!-- End of footer -->
					</td>
				</tr>
			</table>
		</td>
	</tr>
</table>
<!-- End of footer container -->
</body>
</html>